Class Profile3G

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Profile3G
extends Profile
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a device profile that is used as a model of a 3G device when analyzing trace data.

      • energy

        public double energy(double time1,
            double time2,
            RRCState state,
            java.util.List<PacketInfo> packets)
        A utility method for calculating RRC energy.
        Specified by:
        energy in class Profile
        Parameters:
        time1 - The begin time for the RRC state.
        time2 - The end time for the RRC state.
        state - An RRCState enumeration value that indicates the RRC energy state.
        packets - A List of packets that were passed during the specified time period. The packet information may be used in determining the amount of energy used.
        Returns:
        The energy consumption value for the RRC state.
